WEBVTT

00:00.567 --> 00:02.777
Previously on 'Heartland':

00:02.902 --> 00:04.902
Can l have another one?

00:08.341 --> 00:09.910
What's the deal with you, guys?

00:10.010 --> 00:12.877
What, he didn't tell you?

00:13.246 --> 00:14.781
l was married to his daughter.

00:14.881 --> 00:16.315
You're Amy and Lou's dad?

00:16.416 --> 00:17.350
Soraya, right?

00:17.450 --> 00:18.451
Yeah, hi.

00:18.551 --> 00:19.252
Hey, l'm Ben.

00:19.352 --> 00:21.421
l know.
l've heard a lot about you.

00:21.521 --> 00:21.988
This whole time l've been here,

00:22.088 --> 00:25.258
nobody said a word about Lou
or Amy having a father.

00:25.358 --> 00:26.793
l just figured he was dead or something.

00:26.893 --> 00:28.194
Well, he might as well have been.

00:28.294 --> 00:29.963
Oh, my God, Mom, it's Nick Harwell.

00:30.063 --> 00:31.164
Who's Nick Harwell?

00:31.264 --> 00:32.732
Only the hottest jumper on the circuit.

00:32.832 --> 00:33.566
Oh, my God.

00:33.666 --> 00:34.901
What?

00:35.001 --> 00:37.001
lt's Nick Harwell.

